</STRONG><font face=arial size=2><LI><A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=618" TARGET=_self>Re: New Topic: A Return to Innocence?</A> - <b>Lectral</b> <i>2:13 p.m. 10/2/1999</i>
 <SMALL>(14 views)</SMALL> <SMALL><EM>(user-37kbobr.dialup.mindspring.com)</EM></SMALL> <UL>
